93
00:10:05,870 --> 00:10:07,180
Countless times I wanted to give up

94
00:10:07,180 --> 00:10:08,300
and just lay down right there.

95
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:11,110
But

96
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:17,540
every time

97
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:20,750
I turned around,

98
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:26,300
I saw you beside me.

99
00:10:28,110 --> 00:10:28,990
I felt

100
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,180
I could keep going

101
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,110
a bit longer and run a bit more.

102
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:37,180
When I couldn't take it anymore,

103
00:10:38,230 --> 00:10:39,350
I'd turn and look at you,

104
00:10:39,350 --> 00:10:40,780
so I could keep going a bit longer.

105
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:43,060
I can't explain

106
00:10:45,230 --> 00:10:47,420
if it was for you or because of you

107
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:48,900
that I made it to the end.

108
00:10:52,230 --> 00:10:53,270
I feel

109
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,140
one's

110
