whole life

111
00:10:59,030 --> 00:10:59,870
is long.

112
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:03,900
If I

113
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:08,820
have you as a companion,

114
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:11,350
couldn't we,

115
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,060
like today's marathon,

116
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:17,060
see all the scenery,

117
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,350
