118
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:20,470
and make it to the end?

119
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:28,700
What do you think?

120
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:38,780
Say something.

121
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:42,390
Let's

122
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,270
