129
00:12:12,940 --> 00:12:14,150
I hurt myself what?

130
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:16,780
You hurt yourself far worse

131
00:12:17,580 --> 00:12:18,780
than it did to me.

132
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:33,150
Isn't that Zhenhua?

133
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,230
Let's go home.

134
