I don't care. I'm just jealous.

427
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:33,300
Why is she suited and not me?

428
00:32:33,470 --> 00:32:36,540
You're an experienced captain.

429
00:32:36,950 --> 00:32:38,380
You won't veer off course.

430
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:41,580
Handing a ship to you is the safest.

431
00:32:41,990 --> 00:32:43,820
But what I'm doing now

432
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:45,750
