433
00:32:46,300 --> 00:32:47,950
I might discover a new world

434
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:49,950
or hit a reef and sink.

435
00:32:50,470 --> 00:32:51,310
So,

436
00:32:51,430 --> 00:32:53,430
only Huang Yimei can take this risk with me.

437
00:32:55,540 --> 00:32:57,750
When I saw her off yesterday,

438
00:32:58,860 --> 00:33:02,190
I felt her life wasn't comfortable.

439
00:33:02,780 --> 00:33:03,620
Very oppressive.

440
00:33:04,540 --> 00:33:05,380
Yes.

441
00:33:06,470 --> 00:33:07,310
That day

442
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:09,750
when we did our nails together, I felt it too.

443
00:33:10,540 --> 00:33:12,580
So she needs this adventure more now.

444
00:33:13,190 --> 00:33:15,580
But now she has a child.

445
00:33:16,140 --> 00:33:18,030
I'm not sure if she can still

446
00:33:18,580 --> 00:33:19,510
be as free as before.

447
00:33:22,230 --> 00:33:23,510
Ms. Sun, your document

448
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,780
is very well done.

449
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:26,860
Let's end our conversation here today.

450
00:33:33,060 --> 00:33:33,900
Please come in.

451
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:36,140
Hello,

452
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:37,910
I'm the one who got interviewed last time.

453
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,950
Huang Yimei, right?

454
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:43,100
- Yes, yes.
- Come in, come in.

455
00:33:43,620 --> 00:33:44,460
- Have a seat.
- Sure.

456
00:33:46,820 --> 00:33:48,060
How are you? Feeling better?

457
00:33:50,510 --> 00:33:51,350
Not too bad.

458
00:33:52,430 --> 00:33:53,380
You still remember me.

459
00:33:53,910 --> 00:33:54,750
Of course.

460
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,910
The school management discussed

461
00:33:57,100 --> 00:33:58,580
the art therapy proposal you made.

462
00:33:58,780 --> 00:34:00,620
It's very feasible.

463
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:02,060
That's great.

464
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:05,620
Sorry to disturb you so suddenly.

465
00:34:05,620 --> 00:34:06,540
It's a little abrupt,

466
00:34:06,820 --> 00:34:07,860
but I need to ask something.

467
00:34:08,060 --> 00:34:09,510
It's been two weeks,

468
00:34:09,870 --> 00:34:11,950
and I haven't received the interview result.

469
00:34:12,210 --> 00:34:13,060
I wanted to know

470
00:34:13,060 --> 00:34:15,580
if there was something I lacked.

471
00:34:16,180 --> 00:34:17,790
You already passed the interview.

472
00:34:19,580 --> 00:34:20,790
No one notified me.

473
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:22,660
We sent you an email

474
00:34:22,740 --> 00:34:24,740
asking for background check contacts.

475
00:34:25,310 --> 00:34:27,700
Didn't you reply saying you couldn't join us?

476
00:34:29,950 --> 00:34:30,830
I replied?

477
00:34:30,830 --> 00:34:31,670
Yes.

478
00:34:31,790 --> 00:34:32,630
The HR Department said

479
00:34:32,640 --> 00:34:34,620
your husband even called to confirm.

480
00:34:35,180 --> 00:34:36,510
We felt it was a pity,

481
00:34:36,870 --> 00:34:38,030
but we had no choice.

482
00:34:38,220 --> 00:34:40,060
The offer was given to another candidate.

483
00:34:46,950 --> 00:34:48,660
You shouldn't do your nails while pregnant.

484
00:34:48,950 --> 00:34:50,830
Better safe than sorry,

485
00:34:51,350 --> 00:34:52,190
right?

486
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:58,660
My husband said I was pregnant?

487
00:35:07,700 --> 00:35:08,540
Thank you.

488
00:35:31,620 --> 00:35:32,460
Hello?

489
00:35:37,060 --> 00:35:37,900
Hello?

490
00:35:41,060 --> 00:35:42,350
Don't work late today.

491
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:44,430
Come home early.

492
00:35:45,510 --> 00:35:46,390
Is something wrong?

493
00:35:47,390 --> 00:35:48,260
I'll wait for you at home.

494
00:35:50,220 --> 00:35:51,060
Alright.

495
00:36:09,260 --> 00:36:11,580
(Jiaxiang International Middle School)

496
00:37:13,540 --> 00:37:14,380
Where's Taichu?

497
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:16,350
At Yue's house.

498
00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:19,030
Her mom agreed to look after her for a while.

499
00:37:19,510 --> 00:37:20,350
Why?

500
00:37:23,830 --> 00:37:24,870
I have something to tell you.

501
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:46,870
Go ahead.

502
00:37:49,540 --> 00:37:50,430
I want a divorce.

503
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:11,980
Tell me.

504
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,380
Who did you see

505
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:15,870
in Beijing?

506
00:38:24,990 --> 00:38:25,830
Why are you laughing?

507
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:27,100
Does there have to be an external reason?

508
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:31,580
There must be some reason.

509
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:34,220
I don't love you anymore.

510
00:38:46,430 --> 00:38:48,870
You don't love me? That's it?

511
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:51,140
With such a lousy reason,

512
00:38:51,790 --> 00:38:52,870
you want a divorce?

513
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:55,260
Who's still madly in love

514
00:38:56,030 --> 00:38:57,390
after years of marriage?

515
00:38:57,950 --> 00:38:59,910
Isn't it just living day to day?

516
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:01,270
Huang Yimei,

517
00:39:01,830 --> 00:39:03,830
I've treated you well,

518
00:39:04,700 --> 00:39:06,350
maybe not as pampered

519
00:39:06,350 --> 00:39:07,220
as before,

520
00:39:07,990 --> 00:39:08,910
so you just stopped loving me?

521
00:39:09,220 --> 00:39:10,060
Isn't it ridiculous?

522
00:39:16,310 --> 00:39:18,390
I can't give you a son,

523
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:21,950
and you can't give me trust and respect.

524
00:39:23,870 --> 00:39:25,740
We are from two different worlds.

525
00:39:28,830 --> 00:39:30,060
Why force it?

526
00:39:30,700 --> 00:39:31,830
What do you mean?

527
00:39:33,030 --> 00:39:33,870
How about the child?

528
00:39:35,430 --> 00:39:36,740
What about Taichu?

529
00:39:37,180 --> 00:39:38,020
Have you thought about that?

530
00:39:38,220 --> 00:39:39,830
That's exactly why

531
00:39:42,030 --> 00:39:43,430
I must divorce you.

532
00:39:45,620 --> 00:39:47,740
What kind of family is this?

533
00:39:49,350 --> 00:39:50,310
For her mental health...

534
00:39:50,310 --> 00:39:51,220
Shut up.

535
00:39:54,910 --> 00:39:55,750
Huang Yimei,

536
00:39:56,470 --> 00:39:57,540
I'm telling you.

537
00:39:58,510 --> 00:39:59,350
Your decision alone

538
00:39:59,660 --> 00:40:01,100
means nothing.

539
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:03,140
You're not going anywhere,

540
00:40:04,540 --> 00:40:05,380
unless

541
00:40:06,140 --> 00:40:07,870
you never want to see the child again.

542
00:40:10,910 --> 00:40:12,910
This is my first time asking for a divorce.

543
00:40:13,540 --> 00:40:14,660
I understand

544
00:40:14,660 --> 00:40:15,660
you're angry

545
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:16,660
and find it hard to accept.

546
00:40:17,180 --> 00:40:18,020
But Fang,

547
00:40:19,030 --> 00:40:19,950
