548
00:40:21,660 --> 00:40:23,830
I hope we can resolve this peacefully.

549
00:40:24,910 --> 00:40:26,660
If you can't, that's okay.

550
00:40:27,220 --> 00:40:28,350
I'll file for divorce.

551
00:40:30,390 --> 00:40:31,230
In six months

552
00:40:32,870 --> 00:40:33,710
to a year,

553
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:36,060
it'll be over.

554
00:40:37,430 --> 00:40:39,830
I will definitely fight for Taichu's custody.

555
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:42,510
I know

556
00:40:43,100 --> 00:40:44,790
you rejected

557
00:40:47,390 --> 00:40:48,230
the school job.

558
00:40:50,390 --> 00:40:51,870
I also know you installed

559
00:40:51,870 --> 00:40:53,030
a tracking app on my phone.

560
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:01,660
I'm going to pick up the child.

561
00:41:02,950 --> 00:41:04,870
Take your time to think it over.

562
00:41:05,830 --> 00:41:07,260
We'll talk again in a few days.

563
00:41:44,220 --> 00:41:45,060
Daddy.

564
00:41:48,700 --> 00:41:49,540
Daddy.

565
00:41:51,430 --> 00:41:52,990
Why is Daddy upset?

566
00:41:53,470 --> 00:41:55,220
Is he mad at me?

567
00:41:55,910 --> 00:41:56,750
Of course not.

568
00:41:57,910 --> 00:41:58,870
He is just distracted.

569
00:42:17,030 --> 00:42:18,620
Our team's efficient collaboration

570
00:42:18,620 --> 00:42:20,910
ensured the project was completed on time.

571
00:42:20,910 --> 00:42:23,430
Comprehensive testing and optimization

572
00:42:23,660 --> 00:42:26,030
guaranteed its stability and reliability.

573
00:42:26,790 --> 00:42:28,700
We also participated in technical training

574
00:42:28,830 --> 00:42:30,950
to enhance team members'
professional knowledge

575
00:42:30,950 --> 00:42:31,790
and skills.

576
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:33,950
Next week, we will continue to strive

577
00:42:34,030 --> 00:42:35,700
to provide our clients with excellent

578
00:42:35,700 --> 00:42:37,350
network architecture design services.

579
00:42:38,350 --> 00:42:40,220
This concludes our work summary

580
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:41,310
for this week.

581
00:42:44,220 --> 00:42:45,060
Mr. Fang?

582
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:46,750
Mr. Fang?

